Prove the product rules

$
&"(i)" &&nabla (f g) = f nabla g + g nabla f \

&"(iv)" &&nabla dot (bold(A) times bold(B)) = bold(B) dot (nabla times bold(A)) - bold(A) dot (nabla times bold(B))\

